{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_53_03",
  "title": "早坂芽衣",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――七月七日　夜",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……芽衣の誕生日をお祝いするために色々と準備を\nしていたのに、今日はまだ一度も芽衣と話せてませんわ",
      "startTime": 9.8108958562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "この私が一ヶ月買い食いを我慢して貯めたお金で\n買えるだけドーナツを買い込んだというのに！",
      "startTime": 20.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなからお祝いされて今日の芽衣は輪をかけて\nご機嫌で……微笑ましくはありますけど……",
      "startTime": 28.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "私が一番芽衣の誕生日を祝うのを楽しみにしていたん\nですのよ。ここで諦める訳にはいきませんわ！",
      "startTime": 38.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "日付が変わるまでが芽衣の誕生日！\n成宮すず、必ず盛大に芽衣を祝ってみせますわ！",
      "startTime": 46.5223724834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_living-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 52.9996383032
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ～！　みんなありがとう！　えへへ～嬉しいな～\nこれで芽衣、一ヶ月はドーナツだけで生活出来るよ！",
      "startTime": 61.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "両手で抱えきれないほどドーナツをもらってますわ！？\nみんな考えることは同じだろうと思ってはいましたが",
      "startTime": 71.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14933.3333333,
          "startTime": 86.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "私が芽衣の両手をドーナツで一杯にしたかったのに……\nあれだけもらえば、もうドーナツはいりませんわよね",
      "startTime": 81.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.1166852317
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.1166852317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……どうしましょう、この大量のドーナツ……\nさすがの芽衣でもあれ以上ドーナツはいりませんわよね",
      "startTime": 96.5333277385,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11323.340962699987,
          "startTime": 107.8566687012
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.6892949425
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃーん！　おーい！　入るよ！　入るよ！？\nいいよね！？　今日は芽衣の誕生日だもんね！",
      "startTime": 108.9000020345,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7267.373758700003,
          "startTime": 108.9566687012
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.9000020345
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.5226221724
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、芽衣！？　突然どうしたんですの！？\nさくら達にお祝いされていたところだったのでは……？",
      "startTime": 117.5000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.0931893035
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　でも、芽衣、すずにゃんにお誕生日お祝いして\n欲しくて！　お祝いしてもらいに来たの！",
      "startTime": 124.9000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.5265226368
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ね、朝からずっといつすずにゃんにお祝いしてもら\nえるかなってワクワクしてたのに全然会えなかったから",
      "startTime": 132.5666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.0598559719
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.9367950931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、すずにゃん！　今日は早坂芽衣の誕生日だぞ～\n存分にお祝いして、芽衣を喜ばせるのだ～！",
      "startTime": 142.8666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.0265165333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、まるで私達は織姫と彦星のようですわね\nいいですわ、私が芽衣の誕生日を締めくくりましょう！",
      "startTime": 154.299995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.601644135
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "やったー！　ねえねえ、もしかしてここにある笹と短冊\nすずにゃんが用意してくれてたの？",
      "startTime": 165.4333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.7683067327
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、芽衣と一緒にお願い事を書こうと思って\nそれから……そのドーナツもどうぞ。いらなければ――",
      "startTime": 172.4666625977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.8578529363
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "わぁぁ！！　ありがとう！　すっごく嬉しい！\n猫ちゃんの形に～……月の形もある！　可愛いなぁ",
      "startTime": 183.3666625977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 191.224519603
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなに喜ぶものでもないでしょう？\nあれだけ沢山のドーナツをもらっていたんですし……",
      "startTime": 195.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 198.9454039261
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんからもらったドーナツは特別なドーナツだよ\nだって芽衣のことを一杯考えて選んでくれたんでしょ？",
      "startTime": 203.2333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 207.6454039261
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "ねえねえ、月の形のやつ今、食べちゃわない？\n一緒にドーナツを食べると、それが思い出になるんだよ",
      "startTime": 212.1333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 216.2787372594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、いいですわよ。以前、言っていましたわよね\n昔から家族でもよくドーナツを食べていたと",
      "startTime": 221.2333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 225.1868354803
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう！　だから、月の形のドーナツを食べるたびに\n今日のすずちゃんとのことを思い出すんだろうな～",
      "startTime": 230.0666697185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 233.953502147
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 239.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁ、それはロマンチックでいいですわね\nお誕生日おめでとうございます、芽衣",
      "startTime": 239.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 243.2247490571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_53_03-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、せっかくですし……\n短冊にお願い事を書いてからドーナツを食べましょうか",
      "startTime": 245.5567048476,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_write-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4892.806172399986,
          "startTime": 250.44951102
        }
      ]
    },
    {
